Declaration
Simple
declare -a x
Declaration with elements 
x=(1 2 3 a b c) 

Storing a value 
x[0]="some"
x[1]="word"

Retrieving a value 
${x[0]}
${x[1]}
${x[@]} or ${x[*]} returns all values as single items respectively a long string 

Special functions
${#array[@]}
	Count the number of elements in $array
${!array[@]}
	Returns the indices in $array
